tasks.instruction: Fix the TypeError: t.nextMaintenance.getTime is not a function in the Jet Engine Digital Twin project. The error occurs when trying to call .getTime() on a value that is not a Date object. Investigate the codebase in /workspace/shadcn-ui directory, identify where nextMaintenance is being used, ensure proper Date object handling, and fix the bug. After fixing, rebuild and restart the service.
